INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (285,1,'2022-05-08 22:12:04','2022-05-08 22:12:04','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Notre clbration des scnes locales se poursuit avec les DJ TRAKTOR de Palestine, gypte, Liban et Arabie saoudite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":295,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Traktor-20-yrs-middle-east-2-1400x0-c-default-1024x608.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-295\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Palestine, gypte.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Des spots rave populaires.  Parmi cela, La rgion est devenue si subtilement l\'hte d\'une abondance de joyaux cachs.  De plus, originaires du Moyen-Orient, la musique de danse et la culture rave prolifrent dans les lieux phmres . </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Des grandes pyramides de Gizeh aux concerts au milieu de la mer Rouge. Ou aux festivals dans la fort du Liban. Une chaufferie au ciel bleu dans le milieu de Ramallah, Palestine. Les conditions socio-conomiques requises pour construire des lieux. Durables sont au mieux prcaires dans de nombreux pays arabes. La musique de danse vers une approche nomade.  Deviennent des fonctionnalits cls pour les DJ. C\'est peut-tre pourquoi tant de personnes se tournent vers Native Instruments et plus particulirement les logiciels et contrleursTRAKTOR. DJ TRAKTOR de Palestine, gypte, Liban et Arabie saoudite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Makimakkuk  Palestine</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Travaillant sous le nom de Makimakkuk, Majdal Nijim est un artiste musical bas  Ramallah qui ne rentre pas facilement dans une catgorie de production et de performance. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Elle habite de nombreuses formes musicales, que ce soit une chanteuse, MC, productrice, DJ, auteur-compositeur ou pote. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>En 2018, Makimakkuk a t prsent dans l\'itration Ramallah de Boiler Room, avec Mukta-feen,Muqata\'a,Sama\', Jazar Crew, Julmud,Dakn, Oddz et Al Nather (ft. Shabjdeed). </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Quand vous coutez Makimakkuk, le dub rgne. Sa capacit unique  voyager transparente. Entre mes genres apparemment disparates, qu\'il s\'agisse de footwork, d\'lectronique ambiante, d\'afrobeats, de hip hop et parfois de ses propres interventions vocales, l\'est tout autant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dans la rgion depuis 2007 environ, TRAKTOR est devenu un logiciel DJ. De premier plan pour beaucoup, de l\'amateur  la liste A. Les machines de Native Instrument comme le X1.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Makimakkuk travaille actuellement sur un EP</em>. <em>Pour la suivre sur</em> <em><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/makimakkuk/\">Insta</a></em>c<em>liquez ici. Voici le lien vers son portfo</em>lio <em><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/makimakkuk\">SoudCloud</a>.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Liban et Arabie saoudite</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost/soulection-radio-show-547/\">Ecoutez la playlist Soulection</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','TRAKTOR turns 20: Middle East','Our celebration of local scenes continues with TRAKTOR DJs from\nPalestine, Egypt, Lebanon, and Saudi Arabia.','publish','open','open','','traktor-turns-20-middle-east','','','2022-05-08 22:46:25','2022-05-08 22:46:25','',0,'http://localhost/?p=285',0,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (286,1,'2022-05-08 22:12:04','2022-05-08 22:12:04','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our celebration of local scenes continues with TRAKTOR DJs from<br>Palestine, Egypt, Lebanon, and Saudi Arabia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While the Arab world might not be your first thought when considering popular rave spots on a global level, the region has ever so subtly become host to an abundance of hidden gems when it comes to DJs and dancefloors. Mushrooming out of the Middle East, dance music and rave culture proliferate within pop-up venues  from the Great Pyramids of Giza to gigs in the middle of the Red Sea or festivals in the forest of Lebanon and a blue-skied Boiler Room in the middle of Ramallah, Palestine. The socio-economic conditions required to build sustainable venues are precarious at best in many Arab countries, thus pushing dance music and rave culture towards a more nomadic approach. In this way, accessibility and portability become key features for DJs, and this is perhaps why so many look to Native Instruments and specifically&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.native-instruments.com/en/catalog/traktor/\">TRAKTOR</a>&nbsp;software and controllers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Steadily gaining popularity around the region since around 2007, TRAKTOR has become a leading DJ software for many, from amateur to A-list. Native Instruments machines like the X1/Z1 combination or the S2 and S4 controllers in particular, are often favored for easy mobility in pop-up parties and bedroom studios. Ahead of TRAKTORs 20th anniversary, we linked up with some of the regions most exciting DJs to peek through the window of lesser-known landscapes, where dance music and rave culture have become a musical birthplace for many artists.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','TRAKTOR turns 20: Middle East','','inherit','closed','closed','','285-revision-v1','','','2022-05-08 22:12:04','2022-05-08 22:12:04','',285,'http://localhost/?p=286',0,'revision','',0);
